wdi2-SH.STA.FGMS.ZS.def: Percentage of women aged 15–49 who have gone through partial or total removal of the female external genitalia or other injury to the female genital organs for cultural or other non-therapeutic reasons.
wdi2-SH.STA.FGMS.ZS.name: Female genital mutilation prevalence
wdi2-SH.STA.FGMS.ZS.source: UNICEF DATA (http://www.data.unicef.org/);  Demographic and Health Surveys (DHS); Multiple Indicator Cluster Surveys (MICS), and other surveys.
